column2: "Kotoshiro, are you okay?"
"...Why are you here? This should not have anything to do with you."
"1. It's not unrelated!"
"2. We couldn't just leave it!"
"<%me>'s right. It's not unrelated to us!"
"<%me>'s right. We can't leave this be!"

"Because, those things
over there are..."
"Heeh, we tried to catch this planet's Miko but lookie, lookie!"
"Lookie lookie, we caught an unexpectedly big fish!"
"...Dark Falz."
"Don't glare like that, it's scary."
"Scary, scary, scary! ARKS are really scary, huh?"
"Aah, whatever. It's not fun anymore. We got here early to eat the Miko, but it seems she's a hiding coward."
"Yep, a cowardly Miko that no one needs."
"...That's why, everyone."
"We're going to collect, then break everything."
"It's being controlled by Dark Falz?! The erosion shouldn't be this quick...!"
"That is probably the power of that Black Child."
"...But that no longer matters."
"For the crimes of not only trespassing into the Miko's shrine, but also slandering the Miko... I will deliver ten thousand deaths upon you!"
